name: JetSki MotoCross Uphill Race
description:
Get ready for supercharged jet ski stunt ride !!

Skill, stunts, and speed is all what you will need there to kick out death-defying tricks, and boost your jet ski to victory.

Ride your jet ski in exotic world locations with amazing details. Start earning cash by collecting the coins all Over

JetSki Motocross stunt game truly put your Jet Ski riding skills to the ultimate test.
